data.text:
published on 2021-10-01T16:55:10Z

Gazillion years have passed since I recorded a set - this gave me time to collect some sounds which I present to you here. This one is dedicated to my BaBe and my friends, the real ones - those that were there to understand in times of need. Thank you! Huge thanx to: Hypnotizer & Taktyle | Erothyme | Mop Mop,Anthony Joseph | SoDown | Apollyon,K-Freq | Datsik,Snoop Dogg | Dub FX | Spankalicious,Alejo | Mindex | Quanta,EurythmY | Freddy Todd,kLL sMTH | Break Science,Sonya Kitchell | Spankalicious,Alejo | Lukas Nelson and Promise of the Real | Dido | Bad Royale,Wheeto | CharlestheFirst | Frequent | Dafuniks,Particle Man | Joe Ford | kLL sMTH | Noisia | Posij | Deekline,Ed Solo,Phibes | The Caracal Project | Detox Unit | Fugees,Wyclef Jean | Charly Antolini | Jinx In Dub,Peppery | Lutan Fyah | Jpod,Love & Light | Nu Strut | Dirtwire | Somatoast | Jacques Greene | Hidria Spacefolk | Lee Coombs | Plump DJs | Vorso | Kid Blue | Freddy Todd | Rakoon | Stanton Warriors | Deibeat | Soul Of Man,Groove Diggerz | Club des Belugas | Jade Cicada | Dave London | Drumattic Twins | Mr. Bill,ill.gates | Phatworld | Psydewise | Sven VÃ¤th,Si Begg | Jinx In Dub,Snareophobe | Frequent | Ruby My Dear | Globular,Geoglyph | Pete York Without you this set was just 3 hours of empty wav file.
